The '''Embassy of the State of Palestine''' in [[France]] ({{lang-ar|سفارة دولة فلسطين لدى فرنسا}}) is the [[diplomatic mission]] of the [[State of Palestine|Palestine]] in France. It is located in 14, Rue du Commandant Léandri in [[Paris]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mofa.pna.ps/ar/archives/5964|title=Embassy of the State of Palestine in France|publisher=Ministry of foreign affairs of State of Palestine|accessdate=2 February 2017}}</ref>

