b/20140415091904/http://www.logos-verlag.de/cgi-bin/engbuchmid?isbn=1640&lng=deu&id= |archivedate=2014-04-15 |df= }}</ref> * One Thousand and One Georgian Proverbs (ათასერთი ქართული ანდაზა) with Tea Shurgharia (თეა შურღაია).<ref>{{cite web |url=http://evergreen.tsu.ge/eg/opac/record/110463?locg=1;query=%20%E1%83%92%E1%83%98%E1%83%A3%E1%83%9C%E1%83%90%E1%83%A8%E1%83%95%E1%83%98%E1%83%9A%E1%83%98%20%20%20%E1%83%AF%E1%83%94%E1%83%9B%E1%83%A8%E1%83%98%E1%83%93%20;qtype=author |title=ათასერთი ქართული ანდაზა |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208140219/http://evergreen.tsu.ge/eg/opac/record/110463?locg=1;query=%20%E1%83%92%E1%83%98%E1%83%A3%E1%83%9C%E1%83%90%E1%83%A8%E1%83%95%E1%83%98%E1%83%9A%E1%83%98%20%20%20%E1%83%AF%E1%83%94%E1%83%9B%E1%83%A8%E1%83%98%E1%83%93%20;qtype=author |archivedate=2015-12-08 |df= }}</ref> Bilingual, A Comparative Translation from Georgian, (Persian Title: Hezāro yek żarbolmasal-e gorǧī), Publication of Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Tehran 2000.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://buy-book.ir/9789643610197 |title=هزار و یک ضرب المثل گرجی |publisher=Buy-book.ir |date= |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416040914/http://buy-book.ir/9789643610197 |archivedate=2014-04-16 |df= }}</ref> * Shota Rustaveli, Knight in the Panther's Skin, A Georgian National Epic, Translation and Rendering, (Persian Title: Palangīnehpūš), Iran-Jam Publishing House, Tehran 1998.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://buy-book.ir/ |title=بای بوک - خرید کتاب |publisher=Buy-book.ir |date=2009-03-25 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416041601/http://buy-book.ir/ |archivedate=2014-04-16 |df= }}</ref>
